net.wombatrpgs.rainfall.collisions
Class RectHitbox

java.lang.Object
  net.wombatrpgs.rainfall.collisions.Hitbox
      net.wombatrpgs.rainfall.collisions.RectHitbox

public class RectHitbox
extends Hitbox

Standard rectangular hitbox used by 99% of things in this game. It requires knowing the location of its parent as all its coordinates are relative.

RectHitbox

public RectHitbox(Positionable parent,
                  int x1,
                  int y1,
                  int x2,
                  int y2)
Creates a new rectangular hitbox. All coordinates relative to the origin of the hitbox owner.

Parameters:
parent - The positionable owner of this hitbox
x1 - The upper left x-coord, in pixels
y1 - The upper left y-coord, in pixels
x2 - The lower right x-coord, in pixels
y2 - The lower right y-coord, in pixels

isColliding

public CollisionResult isColliding(Hitbox other)
Description copied from class: Hitbox
Decide if this hitbox collides with the other hitbox via any means necessary. This should most likely be heavily optimized, as every event on the map will be spewing these at each other. And in an exponential fashion.
